The paper deals with the formalism of belief revision, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves the study of qualitative algebras (QAs), which is a topic in logic and set theory (cs.LO). The algorithm design and implementation aspects of the paper suggest that it could also belong to the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the study of propositional closures, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC).
